name: Jurassic Zoo : Dinosaur Hunting
summary: Jurassic Zoo VR is a story-driven VR dinosaur survival shooter that puts you face to face with danger. Step into a fallen dinosaur zoo where every mission is a fight to survive. Hunt fast, intelligent raptors, confront the mighty T-Rex, and rescue trapped survivors. Designed for immersive VR combat, you’ll experience intense action, realistic encounters, and nonstop survival gameplay. Perfect for fans of VR shooters, dinosaur hunting games, survival adventures, and action-packed VR experiences.
